<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink372" corresp="#TNV23poem17">
<l>eṉṉu muḷḷiṉaḷ kollō taṉṉai</l>
<l>neñcuṇat tēṟṟiya vañciṉak kāḷaiyo</l>
<l>ṭaḻuṅkaṉ mūtū ralareḻac</l>
<l>ceḻumpal kuṉṟa miṟantaveṉ makaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Has my daughter, </l>
<l>who traversed many luxuriant mountains </l>
<l>inspiring gossips to rise in the noisy old village, </l>
<l>together with the young man of a deceitful kind, </l>
<l>who deceived her, in order to eat [her] heart, </l>
<l>thought about me too? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
